snippet.title: Nitro Kid - Official Launch Trailer | OUT NOW
snippet.description:
Synthwave Roguelike Deckbuilder is OUT NOW
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1709050/Nitro_Kid/

Choose one of the unique Agents.
Use card combos and fight through the floors of INFINITY tower.
Featuring 30+ fresh synthwave tracks by LudoWic, Tonebox and Jules Reves.
And so much more in the full game!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1709050/Nitro_Kid/

Join other Agents on Discord:
https://discord.com/invite/MwGh8SsNKB
